{
  "id": "69f1ad05a3aa7ec103b3d5e9",
  "title": "Wikipedia のダンプ",
  "created": 1777446151,
  "updated": 1777703758,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f1ad05a3aa7ec103b3d5e9",
      "text": "Wikipedia のダンプ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446151
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d53",
      "text": "from [2026/04/27inajobの父のパソコン選び]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446151
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d54",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446171
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59b3d00000000003f7cad",
      "text": "Wikipediaダウンロードしたやつをローカルで見れるようにするとか面白そう[mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703742,
      "updated": 1777703746
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59b3f00000000003f7caf",
      "text": " インターネットのない地域の子どもたちにUSBに入れて配ってる話があった",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703743,
      "updated": 1777703746
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59b3f00000000003f7cb0",
      "text": " Wikipedia 2026 5月号みたいな感じで毎月届けるとか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703743,
      "updated": 1777703746
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59b3f00000000003f7cb1",
      "text": " 田舎のスタンドアローン環境と[ポストアポカリプス]の類似性を感じる[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703743,
      "updated": 1777703746
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59b3f00000000003f7cb2",
      "text": "\t[Wikipedia のダンプ]がある[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703743,
      "updated": 1777703746
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59b3f00000000003f7cb3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703743,
      "updated": 1777703743
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59b3d00000000003f7cae",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703742,
      "updated": 1777703742
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d56",
      "text": "Wikipedia のダンプがある[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d57",
      "text": "\thttps://dumps.wikimedia.org/",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d58",
      "text": "\tzim という独自の形式で圧縮されている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d59",
      "text": " \t[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/ZIM_(ファイルフォーマット) ZIM_(ファイルフォーマット)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d5a",
      "text": "\thttps://dumps.wikimedia.org/other/kiwix/zim/wikipedia/",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d5b",
      "text": "\t\t全 Wikipedia のデータ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d5c",
      "text": "\t\t\t全言語の Wikipedia のダンプデータ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d5d",
      "text": "\t圧縮データで 878.134 GB、画像を削除した圧縮データで 287.515 GB ある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d5e",
      "text": "\t\t画像を削除した圧縮データが有るということは圧縮データの方は画像を含めてのデータということ……。凄まじい。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d5f",
      "text": "\t\t単位合ってるかなー……。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d60",
      "text": "\t\t2年前に110GBでダウンロードできる話をしている人がいたから多分合ってる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d61",
      "text": "\t\t[https://www.reddit.com/r/DataHoarder/comments/1fccptq/did_you_know_you_can_download_all_of_wikipedia_in/ Did You Know You Can Download All of Wikipedia in under 110 GB?]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d62",
      "text": "\t今年中に TB 行きそう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446235
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d63",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446151
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59af80000000000afc4f2",
      "text": "from [2026/04/29]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703672,
      "updated": 1777703672
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59af80000000000afc4f3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703672,
      "updated": 1777703758
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59af80000000000afc4f4",
      "text": "[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703672,
      "updated": 1777703672
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59af80000000000afc4f5",
      "text": " Wikipediaってあんなに大きいのにHDD1個で持ち運べるんだすごい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703672,
      "updated": 1777703672
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59af80000000000afc4f6",
      "text": " \tHDD の容量がデカすぎる[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703672,
      "updated": 1777703672
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59af80000000000afc4f7",
      "text": " \t\tHDDを 1TB として、文庫本の文字数を10万文字/冊とすると、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703672,
      "updated": 1777703672
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59af80000000000afc4f8",
      "text": " \t\t全角文字を2バイト/文字とすると、無圧縮テキストでも50億文字＝文庫本5万冊入る。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703672,
      "updated": 1777703672
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59af80000000000afc4f9",
      "text": " \t\t広辞苑が1500万字なので、50億文字＝広辞苑333セット分",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703672,
      "updated": 1777703672
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59af80000000000afc4fa",
      "text": " \t\t\t[Wikipedia で図書館の禁帯出の棚を作れるくらい]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703672,
      "updated": 1777703710
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59af80000000000afc4fb",
      "text": " \tおおお[1TBってすごく大きい] [vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703672,
      "updated": 1777703679
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59af80000000000afc4fc",
      "text": " \t でもあの図書館よりは少ないんだ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703672,
      "updated": 1777703672
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59af80000000000afc4fd",
      "text": " \t 近くにある市立図書館の22万冊や、札幌の中央図書館の90万冊は入らないんだ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703672,
      "updated": 1777703672
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59af80000000000afc4fe",
      "text": " \t 更に言えば、[Wikipedia は図書館に収まる程度の大きさ]なんだ[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703672,
      "updated": 1777703689
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59af80000000000afc4ff",
      "text": " \t\t 意外と小さい(小さくはない)[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703672,
      "updated": 1777703672
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59af80000000000afc500",
      "text": " \t \t まったく想像できないほど大きいわけではない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703672,
      "updated": 1777703672
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59af80000000000afc501",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703672,
      "updated": 1777703672
    }
  ]
}